    {
      "id": "59e785dd-0366-4a7b-9c6e-82297d45eec9",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Generando `random` values con Java.",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "id": "59e785dd-0366-4a7b-9c6e-82297d45eec9"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "cb2d8bc6-4dba-4186-84e2-40164e9d792b",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "final Random random = new Random(42);\n\n// random.ints(origin, bound) devuelve un IntStream INFINITO [1, 10)\n// Para convertir a array hay que limitarlo primero\nint[] arr = random.ints(1, 10)\n                  .limit(5)\n                  .toArray();\n\nSystem.out.println(java.util.Arrays.toString(arr));\n",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "java",
        "id": "cb2d8bc6-4dba-4186-84e2-40164e9d792b",
        "executionSummary": {
          "executionOrder": 2,
          "success": true
        }
      },
      "execution_count": 2,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": "[9, 4, 1, 9, 1]\n"
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "execution_count": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "11f914c9-ef27-4fee-b259-9a55f29820da",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Probamos los valores generados por `TemperatureTelemetry`, antes hay que modificar la clase para hacerla pública y poder acceder aquí.",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "id": "11f914c9-ef27-4fee-b259-9a55f29820da"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3176dca9-914c-428a-9c17-e481f1654319",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "TemperatureTelemetry telemetry_read;\n\nfor (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) {\n    telemetry_read = TemperatureTelemetry.newRandomTemperatureRead();\n    System.out.println(telemetry_read.toString());\n}",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "java",
        "id": "3176dca9-914c-428a-9c17-e481f1654319",
        "executionSummary": {
          "executionOrder": 13,
          "success": true
        }
      },
      "execution_count": 13,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": "{\"id\":2, \"temperature\":38}\n{\"id\":5, \"temperature\":29}\n{\"id\":6, \"temperature\":23}\n{\"id\":6, \"temperature\":22}\n{\"id\":1, \"temperature\":19}\n"
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "execution_count": 13
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "87b28935-4902-439c-8a1d-89f9efe511ea",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "var path = java.nio.file.Path.of(\"src/main/resources/simple-client.properties\");\nvar props = new java.util.Properties();\ntry (var input = java.nio.file.Files.newInputStream(path)) {\n    props.load(input);\n}\nSystem.out.println(props);",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "java",
