    {
      "id": "1e76d448-28d5-436f-95e8-8d8f87cff58d",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Fakeamos la recogida de la `{\"id\":1, \"temperature\":30}` en el topic `temperature-telemetry`.",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "id": "1e76d448-28d5-436f-95e8-8d8f87cff58d"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b95f539f-8dd5-4469-83dd-328b35ad404e",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "KafkaProducer<String, String> producer = new KafkaProducer<>(props);\n\ntelemetry_read = new TemperatureTelemetry(1, 30);\n\nProducerRecord<String, String> record = new ProducerRecord<>(\n    \"my-topic\",\n    String.valueOf(telemetry_read.getId()),\n    telemetry_read.toString());\n\nrecord.headers().add(\"client\",\"Boas desde java\".getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8));\n\nproducer.send(record, (metadata, exception) -> {\n    if (exception != null) {\n        System.err.println(\"Error al enviar el mensaje: \" + exception.getMessage());\n    } else {\n        System.out.println(\"Mensaje key \" + record.key() + \", value '\" + record.value() + \"' enviado a la partición \" + metadata.partition() + \" con offset \" + metadata.offset());\n    }\n});",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "java",
