      "source": "KafkaProducer<String, com.ucmmaster.kafka.data.v1.TemperatureTelemetry> producer = new KafkaProducer<>(props);\n\nvar telemetry_avro = new com.ucmmaster.kafka.data.v1.TemperatureTelemetry(1, 30);\n\nProducerRecord<String, com.ucmmaster.kafka.data.v1.TemperatureTelemetry> record = new ProducerRecord<>(\n    \"my-topic-avro\",\n    String.valueOf(telemetry_avro.getId()),\n    telemetry_avro);\n\nrecord.headers().add(\"client\",\"Boas desde java\".getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8));\n\nproducer.send(record, (metadata, exception) -> {\n    if (exception != null) {\n        System.err.println(\"Error al enviar el mensaje: \" + exception.getMessage());\n    } else {\n        System.out.println(\"Mensaje key \" + record.key() + \", value '\" + record.value().toString() + \"' enviado a la partición \" + metadata.partition() + \" con offset \" + metadata.offset());\n    }\n});\n",
